# TanStack Router

This project uses TanStack Router with file-based routing.

## Creating Routes

Routes are in `src/routes/`. The router plugin auto-generates `routeTree.gen.ts`.

```tsx
// src/routes/about.tsx â†’ /#/about
import { createFileRoute } from '@tanstack/react-router';

export const Route = createFileRoute('/about')({
  component: AboutPage,
});

function AboutPage() {
  return <div>About</div>;
}
```

## Nested Routes

```
src/routes/
  __root.tsx        # Root layout (TopNav, Sidebar)
  index.tsx         # /#/
  tools/
    index.tsx       # /#/tools
    metronome.tsx   # /#/tools/metronome
```

## Navigation

```tsx
import { Link } from '@tanstack/react-router';

<Link to="/about">About</Link>
<Link to="/tools/metronome">Metronome</Link>
```

## Hash History

Using hash history for GitHub Pages compatibility. URLs are `/#/path`.
